<meta name="assert" content="This test verifies that a position:sticky element with 101% top value does not cause the scrollbar to show when shrinking the height of its container.">

<title><style>
#scroll {
  width: 1px;
  height: 200px;
  overflow: auto;
  background: red;
}
.sticky {
  position: sticky;
  width: 100px;
  height: 355px;
  top: 0%;
  background: green;
}
</style></title>

<p>Test passes if there is a filled green square and <strong>no red</strong>.</p><strong>
